CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Nutex Health Inc is a technology-enabled healthcare services company with two divisions: a Hospital Division and a Population Health Management Division. The Hospital Division implements and operates innovative health care models, including micro-hospitals, specialty hospitals, and hospital outpatient departments (HOPDs). The Population Health Management Division owns and operates provider networks such as Independent Physician Associations (IPAs).
